query:
SELECT c.id, c.propertyId, c.name, c.relationship, c.phone1, c.email1, p.addressLine1 
FROM contacts c 
JOIN properties p ON c.propertyId = p.id 
WHERE c.propertyId IN (1,2,3,4) 
ORDER BY c.propertyId, c.id;
